THE CHOICE IS YOURS
Orginal piece -13,8x11,1cm - acrylic on cardboard
You have the choice to own an original both physically and digitally or watch the physical piece burn as you bake with your digital piece in all its glory. 

in other words: I can ship the physical piece to you, worldwide shipping. 
or; i can send you a video of the physical piece burning after transaction is confirmed.
